  "design_notes": "A carefully paced Medium chart for this energetic track. To stay under the 5.0 NPS limit at 173.3 BPM, we avoid sustained eighth-note streams and use a foundation of quarter notes combined with punchy eighth-note syncopations on vocals and drum accents. Sustained vocals are translated into expressive holds. The drops escalate step density with zigzagging motion, while the outro winds down safely to single steps reflecting the decay of the music.",
